{
  "id": "adv_group_sun_02_04",
  "title": "サニーピース 02 04",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-02-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――星見市、スーパータケミヤ、事務室",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Hoshimi City‚ Supermarket Takemiya‚ office.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "スーパーの店長",
      "speakerNameEn": "Supermarket",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_04-tencho001.m4a",
      "text": "それで、一ノ瀬さんはどうして\nうちでバイトしたいと思ったの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ Ichinose-san‚ why\ndid you want to work part-time here?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.5666664321,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-02-noon",
      "startTime": 6.5666662096
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_04-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "私はダンスをやってるんですけど\nもっと上達するにはレッスン代がかかるので……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm a dancer‚\nand to improve‚ I need money for lessons…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.2666662096,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_04-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "それに、高校を卒業したら家を出るつもりだから\n自立するためにお金が必要なんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Plus‚ I'm planning on moving out after I graduate high school‚\nso I need money to be independent.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.6999995429,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-02-noon",
      "startTime": 22.0666662096
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "スーパーの店長",
      "speakerNameEn": "Supermarket",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_04-tencho002.m4a",
      "text": "親から自立するためか……。ちなみにご両親は\n君が一人暮らししたがってるのを知ってるのかい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To become independent from your parents‚ huh… By the way‚\ndo your parents know you want to live on your own?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.7666662096,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_04-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "いいえ、両親は私のことなんて興味ありませんから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ my parents aren't interested in me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.5333338935,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "スーパーの店長",
      "speakerNameEn": "Supermarket",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_04-tencho003.m4a",
      "text": "そうかな？　一ノ瀬さんを見ていると\nご両親に大切にされてきたんだなって感じるけどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that so? When I look at you‚ Ichinose-san‚\nI feel like you were raised with a lot of love from your parents.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.0666662096,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-02-noon",
      "startTime": 42.8666626492
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_04-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことは……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's not…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.8666626492,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "スーパーの店長",
      "speakerNameEn": "Supermarket",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_04-tencho004.m4a",
      "text": "それで、いつから仕事を始められる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ when can you start working?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.6999967455,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-02-noon",
      "startTime": 48.0666634122
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_04-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "え？　それじゃあ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? So…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.0666634122,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "スーパーの店長",
      "speakerNameEn": "Supermarket",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_04-tencho005.m4a",
      "text": "採用だ\n親離れする前にうちで社会勉強しなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're hired.\nLearn about the real world here before you leave your parents' nest.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.7999969999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichireiroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichireiroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.4833262642
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichireiroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichireiroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.4833262642
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_04-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "タケミヤの店長がそんなことを言っていたんですの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Takemiya-san said that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.5333262642,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_04-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "あの頃の私は、いろんなバイトを経験したわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Back then‚ I tried all sorts of part-time jobs.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.2999929309,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichireiroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichireiroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.1999929309
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_04-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "イベントスタッフ、荷物の梱包、駐車場の交通整理に\n自転車で料理の配達もやったことあるのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Event staff‚ packing boxes‚ traffic control in parking lots…\nI even delivered food by bicycle.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.5333262642,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichireiroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichireiroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 75.5666595976
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_04-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "全部体力のいる仕事ではありませんか\nそんな仕事ばかりだと体を壊しますわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Those are all physically demanding jobs!\nYou'll ruin your health if you keep doing them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.8999929309,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichireiroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichireiroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 83.0333262642
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_04-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "短期で割のいいバイトを探したら\nどうしてもそうなっちゃうのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I looked for short-term‚ high-paying part-time jobs‚\nthat's what I ended up doing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.6999929309,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_04-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "それに、私は人当たりがあまり良くないから\n接客業はちょっと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Plus‚ I'm not very good with people‚\nso customer service is a bit…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.8333272815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_04-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "それなのに店長は私にレジ打ちをやれって言うのよ\nおかげで愛想笑いがうまくなったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But the manager still made me work the cash register.\nThanks to that‚ I got good at faking a smile.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.0999939482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichireiroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichireiroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.8333272815
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_04-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、なんだかんだ言ってタケミヤの店長には\n良くしてもらったから感謝してるんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ all things considered‚ I'm grateful to the manager of Takemiya‚\nhe treated me well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.5333272815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichireiroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichireiroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.9666606148
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_04-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、サニピがデビューしてすぐに\nタケミヤの宣伝のお仕事をやったよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Speaking of which‚ we did a promotional job for Takemiya\nright after we debuted‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.2999939482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_04-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "もしかして、あれは店長さんが\nアイドルになった怜ちゃんのためにお仕事を……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Could it be that the manager gave us that job\nbecause you became an idol‚ Rei-chan…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.0999939482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichireiroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichireiroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122.5666606148
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_04-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "まさか。それはただの偶然よ\n……偶然よね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No way. It was just a coincidence.\n…It was‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.5999939482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichireiroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichireiroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 130.533325247
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_04-rei013.m4a",
      "text": "とにかく、その頃はスタジオを借りるお金もなくて\n自宅の部屋でダンスの練習をしていたのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Anyway‚ back then I didn't even have enough money to rent a studio‚\nso I was practicing in my room.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.0666585803,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichireiroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichireiroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 138.3666585803
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_04-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "そうそう、塀の上で猫ちゃんとひなたぼっこしながら\n怜ちゃんが部屋で踊ってるのをよく覗いてたよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right‚ that's right. I used to peek at you dancing\nwhile you were practicing in your room~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.4666585803,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_04-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "覗き行為を当たり前のように言わないでほしいのですわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please don't talk about peeking into people's rooms like it's normal!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.333325247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichireiroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichireiroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 150.633325247
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_04-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ～。踊ってる怜ちゃんはすっごくかっこ良くて\nずっと見てても全然飽きなかったな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ehehe~. Rei-chan looked so cool dancing‚\nI could watch forever and never get bored~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.733325247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
